requirements for linux-

for ubuntu-

1.JAVA

No need if java is already installed

installation-
1.open terminal.
2.sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/java
3.sudo apt-get update.
4.sudo apt install oracle-java8-installer
5.follow instructions to install.
6.javac -version
7.sudo apt install oracle-java8-set-default

done

2.Python 

No need if already installed

installation-
1.open terminal
2.sudo apt-get install python

done
